## 🛠️ Essential Commands

### Setup & Validation

```bash
# Check plugin dependencies
/checkdependencies

# Set HubSpot API key (store securely)
export HUBSPOT_API_KEY="your-api-key"

# Test API connection
curl -X GET "https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts?limit=1" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $HUBSPOT_API_KEY"
```

### Instance Management

```bash
# Create new customer instance
mkdir -p instances/hubspot/[customer-name]/{reports,data}

# Document portal details
echo '{"portalId":"12345678","environment":"sandbox","lastAccessed":"'$(date +%Y-%m-%d)'"}' > instances/hubspot/[customer-name]/STATUS.json
```

### Common Operations

```bash
# Get contacts
curl -X GET "https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts?limit=10" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $HUBSPOT_API_KEY"

# Create contact
curl -X POST "https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $HUBSPOT_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"properties":{"email":"test@example.com","firstname":"John","lastname":"Doe"}}'

# Get workflows
curl -X GET "https://api.hubapi.com/automation/v4/flows" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $HUBSPOT_API_KEY"
```

