## 📊 HubSpot Conventions

### Portal Management

- **Alias Format**: Use `[company-name]-[sandbox|production]` (e.g., `acme-sandbox`)
- **Instance Directory**: `instances/hubspot/[company-name]/`
- **Status Tracking**: Update `STATUS.json` after each session

### Naming Standards

- **Properties**: Use `snake_case` for custom properties (e.g., `customer_tier`)
- **Workflows**: Use descriptive names (e.g., `Lead Nurturing - MQL to SQL`)
- **Lists**: Include criteria in name (e.g., `Active Customers - Last 30 Days`)

### API Rate Limits

- **Standard**: 100 requests / 10 seconds
- **Batch Operations**: Use batch endpoints when available
- **Retry Logic**: Implement exponential backoff for 429 errors

### Data Quality

- **Required Fields**: Always validate email format for contacts
- **Deduplication**: Check for existing records before creating
- **Data Hygiene**: Use `hubspot-data-hygiene-specialist` agent regularly

