## 🔐 Security

### Never Commit

- API keys or access tokens (`.env` files)
- Customer data or PII (`instances/*/data/`)
- OAuth credentials or refresh tokens
- Internal portal IDs or endpoints

### Required in .gitignore

```gitignore
# HubSpot credentials
.env
.env.local
.hubspot/

# Customer data
instances/*/data/
instances/*/backups/
instances/*/*.csv
instances/*/*.json
!instances/*/STATUS.json
!instances/*/README.md

# API logs
*.log
api-logs/
```

